    M -- No --> L
    M -- Yes --> N[Evaluation\nTest Set: Accuracy · F1\nConfusion Matrix]
    N --> O[Efficiency Analysis\nParameter reduction\nMemory savings vs Full FT]
    O --> P[Visualizations saved to Data/\nTraining curves · Comparison charts]
